text: "You Shook Me" is a 1962 blues song by Muddy Waters and was written by Willie Dixon. It was covered by Jeff Beck and Led Zeppelin for their debut studio album Led Zeppelin and appeared as the third track on the album. ==Notes== Category:1962 songs Category:Blues music Category:Muddy Waters songs Category:Jeff Beck songs Category:Led Zeppelin songs
title: You Shook Me
